Add a link to a diagram (internal function)

Source: R/diagram.R
add_link_internal.Rd

Add a link to a diagram (internal function)

Usage

add_link_internal(diagram, name, from_id, from_type, to_flow)

Arguments

diagram

StockFlowDiagram object

name

Character name for the link

from_id

Integer source ID

from_type

Character source type ("stock", "variable", "sumvar")

to_flow

Integer target flow ID

Value

Modified StockFlowDiagram object
